      "description": "Hey there! \ud83c\udf1f You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d honestly think it just rolled right off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one\u2014the interior is spotless, the paint is glowing, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
