    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring the paint remains deep, glossy, and entirely free of swirls or stone chips. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is pristine. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete binder of records included. Mechanically, it is flawless, featuring a spotless engine bay and a recent set of top-tier performance tires. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a turn-key example that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
      "price": 46500.0,
